  <brief_title>Efficacy of a New Topical Anesthetic</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Single-blind, Randomized, Controlled Trial to Assess the Efficacy of a New Topical Anesthetic in Reducing Pain Associated With Venipuncture in Children.</official_title>
